Description: Python Imaging Library (Avalan PPA pin)
 Pillow is a friendly fork of the Python Imaging Library (PIL); it
 adds image processing capabilities to Python and supports a wide
 array of file formats. This rebuild pins 11.3.0 because Noble ships
 10.2.0 (below floor) and Debian sid ships 12.2.0 (above ceiling).
 The Debian binary name stays `python3-pil` -- the upstream rename
 to Pillow predates Debian's PIL packaging by enough that the short
 name is the long-standing convention.
